{
  "stem": "14897.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, at one point when we were under Russian occupation, my mother went to visit her father, who lived in Wilno.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She left me alone for a month.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I must have been about 13 at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And during that time, there was the deportations of refugees and other undesirable elements.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I had heard about it beforehand and had hidden with a friend I felt was least likely to be-- to be searched for.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish friend, but a local girl, not a-- you see, I knew local people because I went to school-- whose father had been a doctor.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the parents were divorced.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I felt that she was not a member of the intelligentsia anymore, because the father wasn't around.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I survived.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't sent to Siberia by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was very irresponsible, really, of my mother to have left a 13-year-old child for a month during the war because she wanted to visit her father.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she didn't want to take me because I would miss school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, it seems rather a wrong priority.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But anyway, my parents-- to go back to the story-- my parents went to the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as they got there, there was a-- I guess you would call it today some kind of a receptionist and translator.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in-- well, the war between Germany and Russia started in June or July of '41.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this was maybe sometime around August or September of '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So this man, this receptionist, he was a-- he was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he looked at my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Salamon-- this is the man who turned out to have been my father's patient-- what are you doing here?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father explained it to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
